{"tid":1658912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於岑子杰俾對家搞，我地其實可以咁做","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:58:06.000Z","uid":61757,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8e4f8920209708a7580dc7b5d8345a5023dccf","tid":1658912,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:20.000Z","msg":"代朋友開post<br />\n<br />\n大家目睹今晚兇手想奪人性命既行兇手段，再次反映了警察無能力去保護市民。係預計既將來，對家肯定會繼續用殘暴手段令我們自動滅聲，既然如此我地點解唔做預防？<br />\n<br />\n同其中一個帶領民意既人士傾過之後，覺得可以考慮眾籌然後聘請保鏢，去保護一d對家眼中既攪事人士，例如民陣，眾志，陳浩天等，有巴絲話會唔會請錯退休警？但警察都有白警，我地絕對可以做選擇，甚至可以選擇一些因為運動無左份工作既抗爭者/勇武作為保鏢，豈不是一舉兩得！<br />\n<br />\n如同意請推post！我再反映翻意見比佢地！"},{"pid":"58735a938d872e7c55d42f6d11f50cdd1df9d2d6","tid":1658912,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"062f60d43a9d83a7d16ca2d5ee23461fae6eca12","tid":1658912,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"25d7373a3c155bd930b147441ace427653a9f02d","tid":1658912,"uid":61757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4951feea4613cdc55c6ef79dfa5a3c821564beae","tid":1658912,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可唔可以爭爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日美國眾議院通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n你當撚人condom咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過左就唔駛多謝人？<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n條Bill 未過參議院架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n唔該去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n然後講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#hongkonghumanrightsanddemocracyact <br />\n#standwithhongkong<br />\n#fightforfreedom<br />\n<br />\n留意番Representatives 同Senator係有分別，<br />\n望清楚其他人點叫人先好！<br />\n唔好叫人First Name！<br />\n<br />\ntwitter 組已經將議員的tweets<br />\n放左入bot task1<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Srywx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=31b5b238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入<span style=\"color: violet;\"> /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWmYt8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWmYt8Z.png&h=b245ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntask1所顯示的25條tweets<br />\n係嚴重唔夠人<br />\n（大佬呀條條上唔到一千點搞呀？）<br />\n<br />\n最後咪撚再串錯hongkong!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcc451b977d1f126279fa51373d59631cb872ef","tid":1658912,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a>"},{"pid":"7ba3b7a1fdc89fbb463aee2d8286858184c4d5ee","tid":1658912,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"又夾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm